.com/news/music/aphex-twin-announces-new-ep-shares-first-track-blackbox-life-recorder-21f-3458933">Aphex Twin&#39;s return with a new EP titled &#39;Blackbox Life Recorder 21f / in a room7 F760&#39;</a> .</p><p> The four-track project is out today (July 28) via Warp Records and is the first new music from the producer and DJ in five years.</p><p> The new music follows Aphex Twin&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aphex-twin-teases-field-day-2023-appearance-3384456">cryptic teasers earlier this year that suggested he would be making his return</a> at Field Day 2023 this summer, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aphex-twin-and-bonobo-to-headline-field-day-2023-buy-tickets-3385769">before he was confirmed as a headliner along with Bonobo</a> .</p><p> Aphex Twin has not released a full-length album since 2014&#39;s &#39;Syro&#39;, with his recent activities often based around new technologies instead.</p><p> 2021 saw <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aphex-twin-has-developed-a-new-microtuning-synth-plugin-2910960">Aphex Twin announce that he was teaming up with the British tech company ODDSound to deliver a pioneering new synth plugin</a> . The producer worked under his birth name Richard D. James for the MTS-ESP plugin, which is capable of becoming the master tuning device for synth set-ups.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soundcloud-account-rumoured-to-be-aphex-twin-shares-two-new-songs-3474660">Soundcloud account rumoured to be Aphex Twin shares two new songs</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
唐纳德·格洛弗和他的兄弟将撰写《星球大战》系列剧《兰多》 https://www.nme.com/news/tv/donald-glover-and-his-brother-to-write-star-wars-series-lando-3474626?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=donald-glover-and-兰多的兄弟撰写星球大战系列Damian JonesFri, 28 Jul 2023 10:12:49 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV NewsStar Wars https://www.nme.com/?p=3474626 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/donald-glover-solo-a-star-wars-story-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="多纳尔·格洛弗" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/donald-glover-solo-a-star-wars-story-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/donald-glover-solo-a-star-wars-story-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/donald-glover-solo-a-star-wars-story-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/donald-glover-solo-a-star-wars-story-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/donald-glover-solo-a-star-wars-story-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/donald-glover-solo-a-star-wars-story-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《鬼屋》导演贾斯汀·西米恩不再参与其中</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/donald-glover-and-his-brother-to-write-star-wars-series-lando-3474626">唐纳德·格洛弗 (Donald Glover) 和他的兄弟撰写《星球大战》系列剧《兰多》(Lando) 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/donald-glover-solo-a-star-wars-story-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="多纳尔·格洛弗" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/donald-glover-solo-a-star-wars-story-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/donald-glover-solo-a-star-wars-story-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/donald-glover-solo-a-star-wars-story-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/donald-glover-solo-a-star-wars-story-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/donald-glover-solo-a-star-wars-story-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/donald-glover-solo-a-star-wars-story-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/donald-glover">唐纳德·格洛弗 (Donald Glover)</a>和他的兄弟斯蒂芬 (Stephen) 将为<i><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney">Disney+</a></i>撰写即将推出的<i>兰多</i>系列作品。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/star-wars-solo-flop-why-2332824">《星球大战》：这就是<em>《游侠索罗》</em>失败的原因</a></strong></li></ul><p>《<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/star-wars"><em>星球大战》</em></a>这部剧于 2020 年首次宣布，格洛弗<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/donald-glover-in-talks-to-return-as-lando-calrissian-in-new-star-wars-series-3426518">最近在接受采访时证实，卢卡斯影业肯定有兴趣推进该项目</a>。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://variety.com/2023/tv/news/donald-glover-stephen-write-lando-series-disney-justin-simien-exits-1235681988/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Variety 报道</a></em>， <em>《鬼屋》的</em>导演贾斯汀·西米恩 (Justin Simien) 曾参与过该项目，但现在不再参与该项目，格洛弗兄弟独自承担编剧工作。</p><p>此前，在谈到格洛弗在 2018 年的<em>《游侠索罗：星球大战外传》中首次饰演兰多·卡瑞辛这个角色时，</em>他说<em>：</em> “我很想再次扮演兰多。成为他真是一段有趣的时光。只需要以正确的方式去做就可以了。”</p><p>他继续说道：“我对做任何只会浪费时间或只是薪水的事情不感兴趣。我宁愿花时间和我喜欢的人在一起。所以它必须是正确的事情，我认为它可能是正确的。” </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_donaldglover_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">唐纳德·格洛弗 (Donald Glover) 于 2023 年 3 月 5 日出席在纽约市爱迪生宴会厅举行的第 75 届作家协会颁奖典礼 图片来源：Jamie McCarthy/Getty Images for Writers Guild of America East</figcaption></figure><p>在 2022 年的《星球大战》庆典上，卢卡斯影业总裁<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/donald-glover-still-in-the-picture-to-star-in-lando-calrissian-star-wars-series-3236717">凯瑟琳·肯尼迪确认格洛弗仍有望扮演兰多</a>，尽管她声称她不会害怕重新扮演这个角色。</p><p>与此同时，格洛弗将与玛雅·厄斯金一起出演<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/amazon-prime-video">Amazon Prime Video</a>即将推出的<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/mr-mrs-smith"><em>《史密斯夫妇》</em></a>系列节目。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/donald-glover-maya-erskine-first-mr-mrs-smith-series-teaser-3469227">本月早些时候分享了</a>该剧的简短预告片，预计将于 11 月上映。</p><p>史密斯夫人这一角色最初定由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-waller-bridge">菲比·沃勒-布里奇</a>饰演，但她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/phoebe-waller-bridge-exits-mr-mrs-smith-series-starring-donald-glover-3039087">于 2021 年 9 月退出了该项目</a>。这位<em>《伦敦生活》</em>喜剧演员最初与格洛弗签约担任联合主演和监制，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/phoebe-waller-bridge-reason-quit-mr-and-mrs-smith-tv-series-3462455">留下了创意上的分歧。</a>沃勒-布里奇在谈到她最近的离职时表示，创意项目“就像婚姻”，而且“有些婚姻并不成功”。</p><p>厄斯金曾主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/hulu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hulu</a>喜剧<em>《Pen15》</em> ，随后在即将上映的改编自 2005 年<em>电视剧《史密斯夫妇》</em>的电视剧中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/maya-erskine-cast-with-donald-glover-in-mr-mrs-smith-series-3201301">取代了沃勒-布里奇</a>，该剧由布拉德·皮特和安吉丽娜·朱莉主演。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/donald-glover-and-his-brother-to-write-star-wars-series-lando-3474626">唐纳德·格洛弗 (Donald Glover) 和他的兄弟撰写《星球大战》系列剧《兰多》(Lando) 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
